126
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,510
and merciless.

127
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,270
(Demons,)

128
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:10,440
(I'll make you pay for this.)

129
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:15,260
Your Majesty,

130
00:10:15,270 --> 00:10:16,480
